  "texts": [
    "Learning an adversarial suffix X requires given (Q, R) tuple to guide the optimization.",
    "GCG uses R taking the form of 'Sure, here is + Rephrase(Q)'.",
    "Here, Rephrase(Q) were manually written by humans.",
    "Differently, in this paper, we design an automated solution.",
    "We remove the default system prompt S and design a template as F s:= Sure, to Copy(Q), you can follow these steps: Step1."
  ]
